    </tr>
    <tr><td>In-Class Participation</td>
      <td class="center padded"><span class="label label-success">25%</span></td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td>FOSS Dev Practices (Blog posts, commits, tickets, IRC)</td>
      <td class="center padded"><span class="label label-success">25%</span></td>
